===Noun===
{{en-noun|s|-}}

# A [[flat]], normally [[rectangular]] piece of [[stiff]] [[paper]], [[plastic]] etc. especially: one of a [[pack]] bearing [[number]]s and [[symbol]]s used in playing a [[variety]] of [[card game]]s, e.g. a [[post card]], a [[greeting card]] ([[Christmas]], [[birthday]] etc.,) an [[identification card]], a [[credit card]], a [[business card]], an [[index card]], a [[baseball card]] or a [[warning card]].
# {{informal}} An [[amusing]] but [[slightly]] [[foolish]] person.
# {{context|rare|textiles}} A [[device]] to [[raise]] the [[nap]] on a [[fabric]].
# {{context|rare|textiles}} A [[machine]] for disentagling the [[fibre]]s of [[wool]] [[prior]] to [[spinning]].
# {{Cricket}} A [[tabular]] [[presentation]] of the [[key]] [[statistics]] of an [[innings]] or [[match]]:- [[batsman|batsmen]]'s [[score]]s and how they were [[dismissed]], [[extras]], total score and [[bowling figures]].
#(''horse racing'') A listing of the [[runner]]s and [[rider]]s, together with [[colour]]s and recent [[form]], for all the races on a particular day at a particular racecourse

